OL,5, A 96-year-old driver who killed an     
OL,6, 84-year-old pedestrian after being     
OL,7, warned he should not drive by an       
OL,8, optician has been jailed for more than 
OL,9, two years.                             
OL,11,FWilliam Beer pleaded guilty to causing 
OL,12,Fdeath by dangerous driving after       
OL,13,Fhitting Illtyd Morgan on Bedwas Road,  
OL,14,FCaerphilly, on 6 April 2021.           
OL,16,FBeer, of Llanbradach, Caerphilly, was  
OL,17,Fsentenced to two years and four months 
OL,18,Fat Newport Crown Court.                
OL,20,FThe court heard Beer told police Mr    
OL,21,FMorgan appeared "at the last minute".  
